			on the core build platform and contributed performance improvements to
			Next.js, and Software Engineer II at Microsoft, where I built enterprise
			Azure solutions for large partners. Outside of work, I am a certified ski
			instructor at Breckenridge, a Protect Our Winters member, and a volunteer
			with outdoor education programs in Summit County, Colorado. I care about
			climate and environmental stewardship, and I am particularly drawn to
			working with companies building in that space. I take on select consulting
			engagements through <Link href="https://alpinemooseinnovations.com"
				>Alpine Moose Innovations</Link
			> and am open to early-stage investing conversations. Reach me at <Link
				href="mailto:ethan@arrowood.dev">ethan@arrowood.dev</Link
			>.
